class Solution {
public:
    int distanceTraveled(int mainTank, int additionalTank) {
        int totalDistance = 0;
        while (mainTank > 0 || additionalTank > 0) {
            int distance = min(mainTank, 5);
            totalDistance += distance;
            mainTank -= distance;
            if (mainTank < 5 && additionalTank > 0) {
                mainTank += 1;
                additionalTank -= 1;
            }
            totalDistance += (distance / 5) * 10;
        }
        return totalDistance;
    }
};
```

efficiency: HIGH
time complexity: O(n), where n is the number of iterations until one of the tanks is empty
space complexity: O(1)
energy implications: LOW

